Users Preferences\

\f1\b0 This program demonstrates how to save and restore the user's column order and width preferences.  Additionally, all other user preferences -- 
\f2\i font, color,
\f1\i0  
\f2\i switch settings
\f1\i0 , and 
\f2\i window size --
\f1\i0  are also saved and restored.\
