\f1\b0 \cf0 MiscTableScroll supports 
\f2\i in-cell
\f1\i0  text editing.  This example program uses the editing feature to allow the user to rename files.  Double-clicking with the mouse on the file name in the 
\f2\i Name
\f1\i0  column initiates editing.\
\
